            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span><br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/ad8a357fa8480f61f3fe665b69d9c263_7649328915160404433.png",
                "id": "talent10342",
                "key": "Stealthy Bowshot",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Stealthy Bowshot"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span><br>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG. </span>This character gains 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough </span>stacks.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Breakthrough</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br>This state starts with 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough </span>stack. When re-attached, add 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough </span>stack. <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough</span> can have a maximum of 3 stacks.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Gain 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough </span>stack.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br>When the character to which this is attached uses a Normal Attack:</span> If <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough</span> has at least 2 stacks, consume 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough</span> stacks to convert <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt into <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span> and draw 1 card.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/b0033b9dfbdff746cfb03c7b73792a34_5143824766658613543.png",
                "id": "talent97077",
                "key": "Lingering Lifeline",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Lingering Lifeline"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span><br>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Exquisite Throw</span>.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Exquisite Throw</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After your character uses a Normal Attack: </span>Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/f92e763ec4e356d65ffc75d9443b7d22_6406449074195503429.png",
                "id": "talent79485",
                "key": "Depth-Clarion Dice",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Depth-Clarion Dice"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When the battle begins, this character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Breakthrough</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br>This state starts with 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough </span>stack. When re-attached, add 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough </span>stack. <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough</span> can have a maximum of 3 stacks.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Gain 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough </span>stack.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br>When the character to which this is attached uses a Normal Attack:</span> If <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough</span> has at least 2 stacks, consume 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Breakthrough</span> stacks to convert <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt into <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span> and draw 1 card.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/9c5eb94adf31a35a1dcf456b08342b00_383491173723396673.png",
                "id": "talent82307",
                "key": "Breakthrough",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Breakthrough"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_6987969760556086344.png",
                "id": "talent47490",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\"><br>Duration (Rounds)</span></strong></p><p>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds)</span> -1.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_365062790207792285.png",
